# ‚õî FORBIDDEN COMMANDS - ALDRI KJ√òR DISSE

## Destruktive Database-kommandoer
php artisan migrate:fresh
php artisan migrate:fresh --seed
php artisan migrate:reset
php artisan db:wipe

## Farlige Rollback-kommandoer
php artisan migrate:rollback --step=999
php artisan migrate:rollback --step=10

## SQL-kommandoer som krever ekstra forsiktighet
DROP TABLE
DROP DATABASE
TRUNCATE TABLE
DELETE FROM users
DELETE FROM widgets
DELETE FROM user_widgets

## Seeders i produksjon (krever --force flag)
php artisan db:seed --force

# ‚úÖ TRYGGE ALTERNATIVER

